  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="white_box_shadow"><a data-udi="umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1}" title="Japan"><img src="/media/13079415/shutterstock_1101176294_edited.jpg" alt="Ski Bundle Offers" data-udi="umb://media/6d8549dacfe54a2583684882295ffb58" /></a><br />
<p><span class="geolocation-title">£100 off per person when you book your Japan ski trip before 2nd November 2019.</span></p>
<p>If you've been watching the rugby in <a data-udi="umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1c75c362696e43cfabf9211c412d2cd1}" title="Japan">Japan</a> you will have noticed what a beautiful country it is, with its fascinating culture and outstanding scenery. But did you know you can also ski in Japan? The masses of powder 'japow' and incredibly varied skiing mean it's certainly worth a try!</p>
<p>Soak up the culture as well as the slopes with our fantastic itineraries covering our ski resorts: <a data-udi="umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2bdbf008b0b14a6ca3063d783be6cf4d}" title="Hakuba">Hakuba</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1}" title="Nozawa Onsen">Nozawa Onsen</a> and add on a city break to the buzzing capital, <a data-udi="umb://document/c7af808018e443518d3f725c12321904" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c7af808018e443518d3f725c12321904}" title="Tokyo">Tokyo</a> or the traditional and authentic old capital, <a data-udi="umb://document/25c2fbfd78524b50b0b912ebb152521c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25c2fbfd78524b50b0b912ebb152521c}" title="Kyoto">Kyoto</a>.</p>
<p><strong>But why should you choose to ski Japan with Inghams?</strong></p>
<p>• <strong>FREE Lift passes</strong> - included in all holidays<br />• <strong>Transfers and meet &amp; greet</strong> - included in all holidays <br />• <strong>Flexible itineraries</strong> – enjoy the ski then add on a city break<br />• <strong>Bed &amp; breakfast basis</strong> - in all hotels<br />• <strong>FREE ski carriage</strong> - using our preferred supplier, Japan Airlines</p>
